Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未發現針對諾德拉姆的攻擊跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這顯然是有意圖的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的目的多半不是摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是完好無損地奪取諾德拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼防衛部隊足夠應對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以集中全部兵力攻擊敵人要塞？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 而且敵人的戰略
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能更加大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與諾德拉姆強行對接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們所處的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了準備與諾德拉姆對接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切便說得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須趕緊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅伯特小隊 科爾小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應對敵艦哨機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩餘部隊暫時保持距離
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織突擊陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人防守嚴密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來很難摧毀抵禦光子環陣列的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫隊全員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起 我指揮你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即匯合一處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會戰鬥 不論敵人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這機動…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他明明不是X-R
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要 打敗你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打敗你 保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你贏不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法完全成為戰士的你！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今非昔比了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜兵全給我死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要失去冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒隊長那麼成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電磁終端 開始在軌道部署
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會不會一再光顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至多只能發射一到兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部署還要多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使改變角度發射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣還是會被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能指望明日野司令了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射線軸上發現敵機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的極有可能是攻擊電磁終端
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽調機動戰士來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也要守住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據推測那是要塞姿態控制系統的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座要塞為抵禦攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行了整體調頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是說 掩體只能防禦來自固定方向的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為求直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有先打壞姿態控制系統
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間不多 我馬上開始使用祖法爾特火箭炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍敵人就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引住敵人就是了對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗嘗 維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞行動受限
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可以對其造成傷害 趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 實施光子爆破炮的指向發射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人要塞 緊急轉向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被防禦的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 使用機動戰士的推進器轉動要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達 確實敵你不過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓精神頭盔滿負荷運轉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不要命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算得了什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為維甘指引未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達孜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何我也要實現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非實現不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令 您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我回天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們重新組織後 返回戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子環陣列的防線岌岌可危
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支撐不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 請暫時中斷發射程序
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把光子爆破炮的目標設定權交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 由我負責
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾中士 讓出操作席
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知全體機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤離射線軸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸入完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮發射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干涉掩體機能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝擊造成推進系統重創
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人機動戰士開始撤退後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有機動戰士暫時撤離敵人要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待進一步指示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 總算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人要塞的推進系統完全停轉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此下去會和諾德拉姆相撞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即通知諾德拉姆政府緊急避難
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人要塞失去了盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定用光子環陣列毀了它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 連射可能造成艦船無法航行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不發射的話諾德拉姆就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有放手一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就現在 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮 指向發射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵時刻能量不足…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號動力室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入炮擊後功率調整模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人要塞移速放緩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在偏離與諾德拉姆的撞擊軌道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向本艦飛來！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往左緊急避讓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 準備應對撞擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會和敵人要塞一同墜入大氣層
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落地面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難免造成巨大傷亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先逃離要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 集結艦隊全力應對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有作用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用光子爆破炮打開突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 發射系統部件損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要更換發射口側面的共振控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上去換
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更換零件？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…明白了 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 情況明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離進入大氣層 還有180分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更換完成 這樣隨時可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴們的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓你們一死了之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事 滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾米 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧布萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾米 等著我 馬上來接你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…看來回不去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想和奧布萊特成為一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我…孤單一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號是我們的家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們說好要回家的 一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏是我們的家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:14:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答應我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾米… 蕾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜落…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去地球會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆來電
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 還有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進入內部 引爆能量核心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以趕在墜入大氣層前破壞它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 難道想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我 可以救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只有我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一度不知為何而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被焦躁和仇恨沖昏頭腦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 現在我已不再迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心只想保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請允許我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 羅瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 如此下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座達烏內斯會對地球造成嚴重危害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 只能執行備案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 要塞自爆裝置失去控制
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我想辦法搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 直接去能量核心？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照備案 將登陸膠囊投放地球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須在要塞爆炸同時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混在殘骸中 投放膠囊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看準時機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 請交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球是伊甸之地 必須救它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有控制的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-R之力 讓我盡情使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算從內部摧毀這座要塞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 你休想阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但內部構造複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入深處的話 會來不及返回
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用高達撞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:17:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要引爆能量核心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用衛星摧毀器 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是能量核心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我指示引爆位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能失敗的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道伊澤爾坎特大人一早就打算這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到又能並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為維甘的戰士 我戰鬥至今
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為實現維甘的夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事與願違
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人的力量 實在太過渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至於
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是救了許多人的性命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這只是想保住我們伊甸的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球是…伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們決心建造伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為戰爭和疾病受苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你戰鬥的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經連自己為何而戰也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋裏裝滿了對你和父親的嫉妒心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你身在此處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置身險境
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也成了戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有事需要你去完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種捷徑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特 傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞碎片因爆炸進入低空軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對地球的影響降低到最小限度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時確認高達逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入射角固定 進入大氣層
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號隨行進入大氣層
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救亞瑟姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能扔下AGE系統
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我信了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想開創的 維甘的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 為爭奪這美麗的自然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在進行戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.59,0:22:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此赤紅的太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.69,0:23:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一場戰鬥結束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.61,0:24:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球正迎來新時代的變革
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.01,0:24:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.51,0:24:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球圈的動亂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.44,0:24:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.70,0:24:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環繞行星表面的大氣被稱作大氣層
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.58,0:24:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士和宇宙戰艦進入大氣層時
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會發生斷熱壓縮 產生超高溫

